<p>the following afternoon to myself.&nbsp;Concerts were held fairly often and with these and reading I spent the majority of my spare hours.&nbsp;This job lasted for a month, during which time I saw some most ghastly looking wounds being dressed. Christmas day was spent here and I tell you we enjoyed a fine dinner.&nbsp;Roast turkey and ham with boiled vegetables for first course, plum-pudding and custart second, and fruit, nuts and sweets to finish up with.</p>
